      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont really want to go to an er if i can help it... hospitals here are crazy expensive and i just want to get to my hotel. i've felt this kind of tightness before when i'm really anxious about flights. do u think it's more likely just the anxiety from the travel? maybe i can just take some calming meds and rest for a bit?",
