      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll try the ibuprofen. i actually have some diazepam left over from a prescription for anxiety last year, do u think it's safe to take that with the ibuprofen to help me calm down so i can just sleep it off? i just really need to get some rest and stop this feeling.",
